  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to IBus</title>

    <para>
      <application>IBus</application> is an Intelligent Input Bus. It is a new
      input framework for Linux OS. It provides full featured and user friendly
      input method user interface.
    </para>

    &lfs72_checked;

